text.section:
The comparison guide shall:
list each insurer authorized to provide medical professional liability insurance in the State;
include, for each specialty and territory, the base premium charged by an insurer for physicians with policy limits of $1,000,000 and $3,000,000; and
include the base premium charged by an insurer for a:
hospital;
medical day care center;
hospice care program;
assisted living program; and
freestanding ambulatory care facility as defined in § 19-3B-01 of the Health - General Article.
